Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Median duration for 'Accepted + Assigned' activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Assigned' activity across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Difference in average duration between 'Accepted + Assigned' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Earliest start time of 'Accepted + Assigned' across the event log
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Latest completion time of 'Accepted + Assigned' across the event log
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Assigned' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Duration from 'Accepted + Assigned' to the next activity in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Duration from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Closed' in cases where 'Completed + In Call' occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Assigned' before reaching 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases that follow the variant ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Duration variability of 'Accepted + Assigned' across different organization countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + In Progress' in reverse transitions
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total elapsed time involving 'Accepted + Assigned' in the top 5 longest process variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average lead time to start 'Accepted + Assigned' after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + Assigned' before reaching any completion activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'
